(A) Name 5 IT job roles and write one line about what each role does.

      1.  Software Developer – Creates and maintains software applications.
      2.  Web Developer – Builds and manages websites.
      3.  Tester (QA Engineer) – Checks software for bugs and errors.
      4. System Administrator – Manages computer systems and networks.
      5.  Database Administrator (DBA) – Maintains and secures databases.


