(C) Write the full forms and one-line use of: GitHub, Slack, Jira, IDE, API.  

     Full Forms and Uses:
      1. GitHub - (Git Hosting Hub)	
      Use: Used to store and manage code online. 
      2. Slack - (Searchable Log of All Communication and Knowledge)
      Use: Used for team communication.
      3. Jira - (Jira is not an acronym (product name)) 
      Use: Used for project and task management.
      4. IDE - (Integrated Development Environment)
      Use: Used to write and run code.
      5. API - (Application Programming Interface)
      Use: Used for communication between software applications.

